START SERVER 3000
USE MONGODB mongodb://localhost:27017/conformance
SECURITY strict
DOCS openapi
ADMIN enabled

MODEL users {
  name: string
  email: email
  password: password
}

AUTH users BY jwt
AUTH refresh_tokens enabled

ROLE admin CAN *
ROLE user CAN users:read

GET /users FROM users
POST /users FROM users
PROTECT /users

VALIDATE users {
  email: required:email
  password: required:min=8
}

JOB cleanup EVERY 1h {
  LOG "cleanup"
}
